M5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 eztoc-toggle-hide-by-default' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/united-nations-economic-commission-for-africa-uneca-grant-for-businesses-ideas-startups-b-i-s\/#Scholarship_Requirements\" title=\"Scholarship Requirements\">Scholarship Requirements<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/united-nations-economic-commission-for-africa-uneca-grant-for-businesses-ideas-startups-b-i-s\/#Application_Process\" title=\"Application Process\">Application Process<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p>The United Nations Economic Commission for Africa for Business. Idea. Startup &#8211; B.I.S Grant awards $25,000 to Africans with innovative ideas, brilliant startups and growing businesses have commenced. Application requirements are given below;<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"scholarship-requirements\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Scholarship_Requirements\"><\/span>Scholarship Requirements<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Age:\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 16 &#8211; 65 years.<\/li>\n<li>Citizenship:\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Africa<\/li>\n<li>Education:\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 minimum secondary or high school education.<\/li>\n<li>Conferencing Tool:\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Own a good device to initiate a video conferencing call.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"application-process\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Application_Process\"><\/span>Application Process<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Visit <a href=\"https:\/\/unafrica.org\/grant21\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/unafrica.org\/grant21\/<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Select either\u00a0\u2018Inceptor\u2019\u00a0and\u00a0\u2018Custodian\u2019.<br \/>\nNote: An inceptor is for a person who has an idea, concept, or plan but is yet to execute it into business.<br \/>\nA custodian is for a person who manages an existing startup or business.<\/li>\n<li>Be sure to fill the form accurately and expect feedback within 4-5 working days.<\/li>\n<li>After a successful application, selected participants with positive feedback should make adequate preparations for an online interview.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<hr \/>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">To apply for the Scholarship,<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/unafrica.org\/grant21\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"td_btn td_btn_md td_3D_btn\">Click Here to Apply<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"United Nations Economic Commission for Africa (UNECA) Grant for Businesses, Ideas &amp; Startups \u2013 B.I.S The United Nations&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1266,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[14],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1265"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\